1
00:00:38,660 --> 00:00:40,370
Good Morning, Kosuke-onii-chan.

2
00:00:41,420 --> 00:00:43,290
Hey! Good Morning, Chika.

3
00:00:45,040 --> 00:00:46,570
Anything I can help out with?

4
