5
00:02:31,975 --> 00:02:38,470
Sazanami Girls Dorm

6
00:02:38,795 --> 00:02:46,509
TRIANGLE HEART

7
00:02:48,348 --> 00:02:52,763
~ Sazanami Spring ~

8
00:02:59,970 --> 00:03:01,300
Oh man, I'm tired.

9
00:03:02,970 --> 00:03:04,150
Nimura-San..?

10
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,810
Hmm... a little hard don't you think?

11
00:03:10,380 --> 00:03:14,020
Kanzaki... have you been playing with them too much?

12
00:03:14,610 --> 00:03:16,400
Absolutely not!

13
00:03:16,940 --> 00:03:18,740
Will you cut it out?!

14
00:03:20,090 --> 00:03:21,110
Dive.

15
00:03:30,510 --> 00:03:34,330
How many times have I told you not to jump into the bath like that?!

16
00:03:34,530 --> 00:03:36,590
But you always take so long!

17
00:03:37,870 --> 00:03:38,740
Hold it right there!

18
00:03:43,550 --> 00:03:46,100
